msgid ""
"To get things done, plan activities and use the task status.<br>\n"
"                Collaborate efficiently by chatting in real-time or via email."
msgstr ""
"ເພື່ອເຮັດວຽກໃຫ້ສຳເລັດ, ໃຫ້ວາງແຜນກິດຈະກຳ ແລະ ໃຊ້ສະຖານະຂອງວຽກ.<br>\n"
